item.title: CVE-2023-5644|2024-09-25T20:22:12.674Z -- unknown -- wp%20mail%20log
item.description: The WP Mail Log WordPress plugin before 1.1.3 does not correctly authorize its REST API endpoints, allowing users with the Contributor role to view and delete data that should only be accessible to Admin users.
